xrdp (0.9.0~git20150901+dfsg-1~beta1) teckids; urgency=medium

  [ Dominik George ]
  * Decouple xrdp and xrdp-sesman services
    - move /var/run/xrdp directory to xrdp
    - start xrdp as user xrdp

  [ Thorsten Glaser ]
  * Update from upstream git; drop merged patch
  * Improve service descriptions
  * Split xorgxrdp into a separate package with appropriate Depends
  * Add NEWS file documenting the default now being xorgxrdp,
    asking the admin to review configs and ensure packages are installed,
    and documenting that SESMAN_START is ignored by systemd
  * Document RESTART_ON_UPGRADE is now obsolete (always "no")
  * Fix several more warnings and do not underlink libraries

